00346       void operator()(char const *str, char const *end) const {
00347         display_string("set_ttl");
00348         char *end_ptr;
00349         double ttl = strtod(str, &end_ptr);
00350         String unit_str = String(end_ptr, end-end_ptr);
00351         std::transform(unit_str.begin(), unit_str.end(), unit_str.begin(),
00352                        ::tolower);
00353         if (unit_str.find_first_of("month") == 0)
00354           state.cf->ttl = (time_t)(ttl * 2592000.0);
00355         else if (unit_str.find_first_of("week") == 0)
00356           state.cf->ttl = (time_t)(ttl * 604800.0);
00357         else if (unit_str.find_first_of("day") == 0)
00358           state.cf->ttl = (time_t)(ttl * 86400.0);
00359         else if (unit_str.find_first_of("hour") == 0)
00360           state.cf->ttl = (time_t)(ttl * 3600.0);
00361         else if (unit_str.find_first_of("minute") == 0)
00362           state.cf->ttl = (time_t)(ttl * 60.0);
00363         else
00364           state.cf->ttl = (time_t)ttl;
00365       }

00812     struct scan_set_relop {
00813       scan_set_relop(hql_interpreter_state &state_, int relop_)
00814         : state(state_), relop(relop_) { }
00815       void operator()(char const *str, char const *end) const {
00816         process();
00817       }
00818       void operator()(const char c) const {
00819         process();
00820       }
00821       void process() const {
00822         display_string("scan_set_relop");
00823         if (state.scan.current_timestamp_set) {
00824           if (relop == RELOP_EQ) {
00825             if (state.scan.start_time_set || state.scan.end_time_set)
00826               HT_THROW(Error::HQL_PARSE_ERROR, "Bad timestamp expression");
00827             state.scan.start_time = state.scan.current_timestamp;
00828             state.scan.start_time_set = true;
00829             state.scan.end_time = state.scan.current_timestamp;
00830             state.scan.end_time_set = true;
00831           }
00832           else if (relop == RELOP_GT) {
00833             if (state.scan.end_time_set ||
00834                 (state.scan.start_time_set &&
00835                  state.scan.start_time >= state.scan.current_timestamp))
00836               HT_THROW(Error::HQL_PARSE_ERROR, "Bad timestamp expression");
00837             state.scan.end_time = state.scan.current_timestamp;
00838             state.scan.end_time_set = true;
00839           }
00840           else if (relop == RELOP_GE) {
00841             if (state.scan.end_time_set ||
00842                 (state.scan.start_time_set &&
00843                  state.scan.start_time > state.scan.current_timestamp))
00844               HT_THROW(Error::HQL_PARSE_ERROR, "Bad timestamp expression");
00845             state.scan.end_time = state.scan.current_timestamp+1;
00846             state.scan.end_time_set = true;
00847           }
00848           else if (relop == RELOP_LT) {
00849             if (state.scan.start_time_set ||
00850                 (state.scan.end_time_set &&
00851                  state.scan.end_time <= (state.scan.current_timestamp+1)))
00852               HT_THROW(Error::HQL_PARSE_ERROR, "Bad timestamp expression");
00853             state.scan.start_time = state.scan.current_timestamp+1;
00854             state.scan.start_time_set = true;
00855           }
00856           else if (relop == RELOP_LE) {
00857             if (state.scan.start_time_set ||
00858                 (state.scan.end_time_set &&
00859                  state.scan.end_time <= state.scan.current_timestamp))
00860               HT_THROW(Error::HQL_PARSE_ERROR, "Bad timestamp expression");
00861             state.scan.start_time = state.scan.current_timestamp;
00862             state.scan.start_time_set = true;
00863           }
00864           else if (relop == RELOP_SW) {
00865             HT_THROW(Error::HQL_PARSE_ERROR,
00866                      "Invalid timestamp operator (=^)");
00867           }
00868           state.scan.current_timestamp_set = false;
00869           state.scan.current_relop = 0;
00870         }
00871         else if (state.scan.current_rowkey_set) {
00872           HT_EXPECT(state.scan.current_rowkey_set, Error::FAILED_EXPECTATION);
00873           if (relop == RELOP_EQ) {
00874             state.scan.current_ri.set_start(state.scan.current_rowkey, true);
00875             state.scan.current_ri.set_end(state.scan.current_rowkey, true);
00876           }
00877           else if (relop == RELOP_LT)
00878             state.scan.current_ri.set_start(state.scan.current_rowkey, false);
00879           else if (relop == RELOP_LE)
00880             state.scan.current_ri.set_start(state.scan.current_rowkey, true);
00881           else if (relop == RELOP_GT)
00882             state.scan.current_ri.set_end(state.scan.current_rowkey, false);
00883           else if (relop == RELOP_GE)
00884             state.scan.current_ri.set_end(state.scan.current_rowkey, true);
00885           else if (relop == RELOP_SW) {
00886             HT_THROW(Error::HQL_PARSE_ERROR,
00887                      "Bad use of starts with operator (=^)");
00888           }
00889           state.scan.current_rowkey_set = false;
00890           state.scan.current_relop = 0;
00891         }
00892         else if (state.scan.current_cell_row != "" && state.scan.current_ci.empty()) {
00893           if (relop == RELOP_EQ) {
00894             state.scan.current_ci.set_start(state.scan.current_cell_row, state.scan.current_cell_column, true);
00895             state.scan.current_ci.set_end(state.scan.current_cell_row, state.scan.current_cell_column, true);
00896           }
00897           else if (relop == RELOP_LT)
00898             state.scan.current_ci.set_start(state.scan.current_cell_row, state.scan.current_cell_column, false);
00899           else if (relop == RELOP_LE)
00900             state.scan.current_ci.set_start(state.scan.current_cell_row, state.scan.current_cell_column, true);
00901           else if (relop == RELOP_GT)
00902             state.scan.current_ci.set_end(state.scan.current_cell_row, state.scan.current_cell_column, false);
00903           else if (relop == RELOP_GE)
00904             state.scan.current_ci.set_end(state.scan.current_cell_row, state.scan.current_cell_column, true);
00905           else if (relop == RELOP_SW) {

01081       set_delete_timestamp(hql_interpreter_state &state_) : state(state_) { }
01082       void operator()(char const *str, char const *end) const {
01083         display_string("set_delete_timestamp");
01084         time_t t = timegm(&state.tmval);
01085         if (t == (time_t)-1)
01086           HT_THROW(Error::HQL_PARSE_ERROR, String("DELETE invalid timestamp."));
01087         state.delete_time = (uint64_t)t * 1000000000LL + state.nanoseconds;
01088         memset(&state.tmval, 0, sizeof(state.tmval));
01089         state.nanoseconds = 0;
01090       }
01091       hql_interpreter_state &state;
01092     };

01094     struct set_scanner_id {
01095       set_scanner_id(hql_interpreter_state &state_) : state(state_) { }
01096       void operator()(char const *str, char const *end) const {
01097         display_string("set_scanner_id");
01098         state.scanner_id = (uint32_t)strtol(str, 0, 10);
01099       }
01100       hql_interpreter_state &state;
01101     };
